    "As such, the various types of cameras along with their operational range in nanometre are RedEye 1.7 (950-1700) nm, RedEye 2.2 (1200-2200) nm, BlackEye (2900-4200) nm, BlueEye (220-380) nm, GreenEye (400-1000) nm and OrangeEye (580-1000) nm (Niedermaier et al., 2019).",
